name: PlayStation Underground: Jampack Summer 2003
synopsis: A collection of demos from the Official PlayStation Magazine. The disc contains demos of [[Amplitude]], [[ATV Offroad Fury 2]], [[The Getaway]], [[MLB 2004]], [[Primal]], [[Silent Hill 3]], [[War of the Monsters]] and [[World Tour Soccer 2003]] as well as videos of [[Downhill Domination]], [[Jak II]], [[NBA Street Vol. 2]], [[Rise to Honor]] and [[Syphon Filter: The Omega Strain]].
